title: 86. America: What The F*ck Is Going On?!
itunes:title: 86. America: What The F*ck Is Going On?!
description: To see the truth, you have to detach yourself from your previous views and beliefs. On today's episode, Andy and the crew talk about what's going on with the election results, how to stay calm in these uncertain times, and how you can seek the truth for yourself.
